<template>
    <el-form :model="ruleForm" :rules="rules" ref="ruleForm" label-width="100px" class="demo-ruleForm">
      <el-form-item label="环境" prop="env">
        <el-select v-model="ruleForm.env" placeholder="请选环境">
          <el-option label="国内" value="guonei"></el-option>
          <el-option label="海外" value="haiwai"></el-option>
        </el-select>
      </el-form-item>
      <el-form-item label="执行方式" prop="method">
        <el-select v-model="ruleForm.method" placeholder="请选择执行方式">
          <el-option label="事件验证" value="events"></el-option>
          <el-option label="事件和属性验证" value="events&properties"></el-option>
        </el-select>
      </el-form-item>
      <!-- <el-form-item label="即时配送" prop="delivery">
        <el-switch v-model="ruleForm.delivery"></el-switch>
      </el-form-item> -->
      <el-form-item label="活动性质" prop="type">
        <el-checkbox-group v-model="ruleForm.type">
          <el-checkbox label="美食/餐厅线上活动" name="type"></el-checkbox>
          <el-checkbox label="地推活动" name="type"></el-checkbox>
          <el-checkbox label="线下主题活动" name="type"></el-checkbox>
          <el-checkbox label="单纯品牌曝光" name="type"></el-checkbox>
        </el-checkbox-group>
      </el-form-item>
      <el-form-item label="特殊资源" prop="resource">
        <el-radio-group v-model="ruleForm.resource">
          <el-radio label="线上品牌商赞助"></el-radio>
          <el-radio label="线下场地免费"></el-radio>
        </el-radio-group>
      </el-form-item>
      <el-form-item label="活动形式" prop="desc">
        <el-input type="textarea" v-model="ruleForm.desc"></el-input>
      </el-form-item>
      <el-form-item>
        <el-button type="primary" @click="submitForm('ruleForm')">立即创建</el-button>
        <el-button @click="resetForm('ruleForm')">重置</el-button>
      </el-form-item>
   </el-form>
</template>
<script>
  export default {
    name: "pointTestTools",
    data() {
      return {
        ruleForm: {
          env: '',
          method: '',
          type: [],
          resource: '',
          desc: ''
        },
        rules: {
          env: [
            { required: true, message: '请选择环境', trigger: 'change' }
          ],
          method: [
            { required: true, message: '请选择执行方式', trigger: 'change' }
          ],
          type: [
            { type: 'array', required: true, message: '请至少选择一个活动性质', trigger: 'change' }
          ],
          resource: [
            { required: true, message: '请选择活动资源', trigger: 'change' }
          ],
          desc: [
            { required: true, message: '请填写活动形式', trigger: 'blur' }
          ]
        }
      };
    },
    methods: {
      submitForm(formName) {
        this.$refs[formName].validate((valid) => {
          if (valid) {
            alert('submit!');
          } else {
            console.log('error submit!!');
            return false;
          }
        });
      },
      resetForm(formName) {
        this.$refs[formName].resetFields();
      }
    }
  }
</script>
